c0000000
00:00:01.330 --> 00:00:02.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000001
00:00:03.080 --> 00:00:06.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You must go to Aureole
and speak with Himmel.</b></Default>

c0000002
00:00:08.550 --> 00:00:09.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FLAMME, FRIEREN]
"On the very northernmost</b></Default>

c0000003
00:00:09.930 --> 00:00:11.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>end of the continent</b></Default>

c0000004
00:00:11.680 --> 00:00:12.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I arrived at the place</b></Default>

c0000005
00:00:12.970 --> 00:00:14.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the people
of this world call Heaven."</b></Default>

c0000006
00:00:15.650 --> 00:00:17.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FLAMME]
"I now know it as Aureole,</b></Default>

c0000007
00:00:18.400 --> 00:00:20.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the land where souls rest."</b></Default>

c0000008
00:00:21.190 --> 00:00:23.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"Many spirits
have gathered there.</b></Default>

c0000009
00:00:24.060 --> 00:00:27.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I spoke with friends
whom I once fought alongside."</b></Default>

c0000010
00:00:28.240 --> 00:00:29.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[birds chirping]</b></Default>

c0000011
00:00:31.070 --> 00:00:32.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
Forgive me.</b></Default>

c0000012
00:00:32.660 --> 00:00:34.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You have a long journey ahead.</b></Default>

c0000013
00:00:35.670 --> 00:00:37.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It took the four of us
ten years.</b></Default>

c0000014
00:00:38.040 --> 00:00:39.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000015
00:00:40.370 --> 00:00:41.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see.</b></Default>

c0000016
00:00:41.540 --> 00:00:43.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, we'll be following
the same route you took</b></Default>

c0000017
00:00:43.830 --> 00:00:46.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to the Demon King's castle
on your first journey.</b></Default>

c0000018
00:00:50.300 --> 00:00:51.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[inhales]</b></Default>

c0000019
00:00:57.230 --> 00:00:58.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That we will.</b></Default>

c0000020
00:00:59.190 --> 00:01:01.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Another brief,
ten-year adventure.</b></Default>

c0000021
00:01:02.060 --> 00:01:03.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000022
00:01:03.520 --> 00:01:05.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One one-hundredth, eh?</b></Default>

c0000023
00:01:05.990 --> 00:01:06.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000024
00:01:07.650 --> 00:01:10.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL] Frieren. You won't be
staying in the royal capital?</b></Default>

c0000025
00:01:11.610 --> 00:01:12.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
I'm going to keep traveling.</b></Default>

c0000026
00:01:13.450 --> 00:01:14.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HIMMEL]
All by yourself?</b></Default>

c0000027
00:01:14.570 --> 00:01:15.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FREIREN]
It's easier that way.</b></Default>

c0000028
00:01:16.870 --> 00:01:19.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN] You're not going to
take on an apprentice?</b></Default>

c0000029
00:01:19.620 --> 00:01:22.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A journey is better
with someone to talk to.</b></Default>

c0000030
00:01:22.830 --> 00:01:24.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I fear it would be
a waste of time.</b></Default>

c0000031
00:01:25.090 --> 00:01:26.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No matter
how much I teach them,</b></Default>

c0000032
00:01:26.550 --> 00:01:27.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>they'll surely die.</b></Default>

c0000033
00:01:28.170 --> 00:01:29.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Heiter and Himmel smiling]</b></Default>

c0000034
00:01:30.380 --> 00:01:31.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
How cheery.</b></Default>

c0000035
00:01:32.170 --> 00:01:34.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's not
how relationships work.</b></Default>

c0000036
00:01:35.100 --> 00:01:36.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's how they work for me.</b></Default>

c0000037
00:01:37.140 --> 00:01:38.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just consider our adventure.</b></Default>

c0000038
00:01:39.140 --> 00:01:41.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's taken up less than one
one-hundredth of my life.</b></Default>

c0000039
00:01:43.270 --> 00:01:45.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sounds like me, I suppose.</b></Default>

c0000040
00:01:46.030 --> 00:01:48.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]
It's funny, don't you think?</b></Default>

c0000041
00:01:49.780 --> 00:01:50.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is?</b></Default>

c0000042
00:01:51.820 --> 00:01:53.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How much
that one one-hundredth</b></Default>

c0000043
00:01:54.700 --> 00:01:55.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>has changed you.</b></Default>

c0000044
00:02:08.550 --> 00:02:09.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
Goodbye for now.</b></Default>

c0000045
00:02:10.460 --> 00:02:11.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm. For now.</b></Default>

c0000046
00:02:11.710 --> 00:02:14.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000047
00:02:20.060 --> 00:02:22.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In comparison, for me,
our journey's been one half.</b></Default>

c0000048
00:02:22.890 --> 00:02:23.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000049
00:02:24.390 --> 00:02:26.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've spent one half of my life
with you.</b></Default>

c0000050
00:02:26.860 --> 00:02:27.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[smiling]</b></Default>

c0000051
00:02:29.070 --> 00:02:30.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] It's going to be
much more than that</b></Default>

c0000052
00:02:30.860 --> 00:02:31.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from here on.</b></Default>

c0000053
00:04:07.250 --> 00:04:09.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HEITER] Take these words
to heart, Fern.</b></Default>

c0000054
00:04:09.830 --> 00:04:11.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Before long,
Frieren will be the one</b></Default>

c0000055
00:04:12.000 --> 00:04:13.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in charge of you.</b></Default>

c0000056
00:04:13.080 --> 00:04:14.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Listen to her
and be a good girl.</b></Default>

c0000057
00:04:16.140 --> 00:04:17.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you don't...</b></Default>

c0000058
00:04:18.180 --> 00:04:19.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I don't, what?</b></Default>

c0000059
00:04:20.010 --> 00:04:22.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll come back as a ghost
and haunt you.</b></Default>

c0000060
00:04:23.430 --> 00:04:25.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

c0000061
00:04:26.400 --> 00:04:27.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So just to make certain,</b></Default>

c0000062
00:04:27.940 --> 00:04:29.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you're saying
that if I'm a bad girl,</b></Default>

c0000063
00:04:29.730 --> 00:04:31.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you'll pay me a visit
after you're gone?</b></Default>

c0000064
00:04:31.850 --> 00:04:32.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000065
00:04:34.310 --> 00:04:35.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[smiles]</b></Default>

c0000066
00:04:36.360 --> 00:04:38.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've grown into quite the sly
young lady.</b></Default>

c0000067
00:04:39.240 --> 00:04:40.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wherever did you pick that up?</b></Default>

c0000068
00:04:42.780 --> 00:04:44.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I take it back.</b></Default>

c0000069
00:04:45.750 --> 00:04:47.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you're
on your best behavior,</b></Default>

c0000070
00:04:47.920 --> 00:04:49.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then I might be willing
to stop by</b></Default>

c0000071
00:04:49.960 --> 00:04:52.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and say hello
every now and again.</b></Default>

c0000072
00:04:57.260 --> 00:04:59.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We should be arriving
at the village soon.</b></Default>

c0000073
00:05:00.010 --> 00:05:01.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000074
00:05:01.800 --> 00:05:02.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was fast.</b></Default>

c0000075
00:05:04.340 --> 00:05:05.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's that?</b></Default>

c0000076
00:05:05.640 --> 00:05:07.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nothing very important.</b></Default>

c0000077
00:05:09.980 --> 00:05:11.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wheels rattling]</b></Default>

c0000078
00:05:11.440 --> 00:05:14.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000079
00:05:26.540 --> 00:05:27.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FEMALE SHOPKEEPER 5A]
Greetings, adventurers.</b></Default>

c0000080
00:05:27.960 --> 00:05:29.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Heading to the mountain pass?</b></Default>

c0000081
00:05:30.080 --> 00:05:31.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wouldn't if I were you.</b></Default>

c0000082
00:05:32.120 --> 00:05:34.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Several people have gone
missing there recently.</b></Default>

c0000083
00:05:35.510 --> 00:05:36.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Killed by monsters?</b></Default>

c0000084
00:05:37.220 --> 00:05:39.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They were taken by ghosts,
according to all of the rumors.</b></Default>

c0000085
00:05:40.550 --> 00:05:42.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Folks have seen them
with their own eyes.</b></Default>

c0000086
00:05:42.590 --> 00:05:43.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Could be the undead.</b></Default>

c0000087
00:05:44.340 --> 00:05:46.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you know
what these ghosts look like?</b></Default>

c0000088
00:05:46.770 --> 00:05:48.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've been too scared to ask.</b></Default>

c0000089
00:05:48.770 --> 00:05:49.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But if you're that curious,</b></Default>

c0000090
00:05:50.020 --> 00:05:51.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>there are plenty
who could tell you.</b></Default>

c0000091
00:05:51.850 --> 00:05:54.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000092
00:06:02.530 --> 00:06:03.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Here's what we've learned.</b></Default>

c0000093
00:06:04.690 --> 00:06:05.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The ghosts take on the form</b></Default>

c0000094
00:06:05.870 --> 00:06:08.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of the beholder's
dead family member or friend.</b></Default>

c0000095
00:06:08.790 --> 00:06:10.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They look just as they did
in life.</b></Default>

c0000096
00:06:11.750 --> 00:06:13.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A couple of witnesses
even claim</b></Default>

c0000097
00:06:13.450 --> 00:06:14.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that the ghosts spoke to them.</b></Default>

c0000098
00:06:16.090 --> 00:06:18.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We can conclude this isn't
the work of the undead.</b></Default>

c0000099
00:06:19.420 --> 00:06:20.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
How are you so sure?</b></Default>

c0000100
00:06:21.840 --> 00:06:23.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[MALE TOWNSPERSON 5A] I did.
-[TOWNSPERSON 5B] No chance.</b></Default>

c0000101
00:06:23.460 --> 00:06:25.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
The undead are merely corpses</b></Default>

c0000102
00:06:25.100 --> 00:06:26.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>being controlled by magic.</b></Default>

c0000103
00:06:27.470 --> 00:06:29.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Things like zombies
and skeletons.</b></Default>

c0000104
00:06:31.850 --> 00:06:34.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But our specters are reported
to appear as they did in life.</b></Default>

c0000105
00:06:35.570 --> 00:06:37.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A reanimated corpse
couldn't do that.</b></Default>

c0000106
00:06:38.400 --> 00:06:39.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All that to say we're dealing</b></Default>

c0000107
00:06:39.820 --> 00:06:42.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with another type of monster
entirely.</b></Default>

c0000108
00:06:44.110 --> 00:06:46.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Seems you know
what monster that might be.</b></Default>

c0000109
00:06:47.620 --> 00:06:48.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, a nasty one.</b></Default>

c0000110
00:06:49.330 --> 00:06:51.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'd best be careful
to avoid it.</b></Default>

c0000111
00:06:55.090 --> 00:06:56.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll take our leave
first thing in the morning.</b></Default>

c0000112
00:06:57.800 --> 00:06:58.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But Mistress Frieren,</b></Default>

c0000113
00:06:59.710 --> 00:07:01.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's clear the villagers
need our help.</b></Default>

c0000114
00:07:02.460 --> 00:07:04.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're starting to sound just
like Himmel and the others.</b></Default>

c0000115
00:07:05.390 --> 00:07:07.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The biggest difference
between you and me</b></Default>

c0000116
00:07:07.390 --> 00:07:08.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is that I am a good girl.</b></Default>

c0000117
00:07:09.310 --> 00:07:10.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All right.</b></Default>

c0000118
00:07:11.010 --> 00:07:12.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you want to help them,
we shall.</b></Default>

c0000119
00:07:13.760 --> 00:07:15.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll be traveling through
the mountain pass either way.</b></Default>

c0000120
00:07:17.820 --> 00:07:19.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[water burbling]</b></Default>

c0000121
00:07:31.580 --> 00:07:34.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The missing villagers
didn't vanish into thin air.</b></Default>

c0000122
00:07:36.130 --> 00:07:37.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Plenty of clues.</b></Default>

c0000123
00:07:38.790 --> 00:07:40.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A generous monster.</b></Default>

c0000124
00:07:41.250 --> 00:07:43.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There are signs of magic usage
all around us.</b></Default>

c0000125
00:07:44.460 --> 00:07:45.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, indeed.</b></Default>

c0000126
00:07:45.760 --> 00:07:47.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can you tell what type it was?</b></Default>

c0000127
00:07:48.390 --> 00:07:49.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Illusion magic.</b></Default>

c0000128
00:07:50.760 --> 00:07:52.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
In my book on magical ecology,</b></Default>

c0000129
00:07:52.970 --> 00:07:54.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>there's this creature.</b></Default>

c0000130
00:07:54.890 --> 00:07:57.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It uses lifelike illusions
to lure in its prey.</b></Default>

c0000131
00:07:58.400 --> 00:07:59.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Einsam.</b></Default>

c0000132
00:08:00.270 --> 00:08:01.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh!</b></Default>

c0000133
00:08:01.230 --> 00:08:03.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It preys exclusively
upon people,</b></Default>

c0000134
00:08:03.270 --> 00:08:05.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>using craftiness
rather than strength</b></Default>

c0000135
00:08:05.200 --> 00:08:07.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to lure in
its unsuspecting meals.</b></Default>

c0000136
00:08:08.700 --> 00:08:11.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It tricks its victims
with phantoms of the dead.</b></Default>

c0000137
00:08:12.370 --> 00:08:13.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
And they really fall for that?</b></Default>

c0000138
00:08:15.170 --> 00:08:16.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Who wouldn't want
a final moment</b></Default>

c0000139
00:08:16.500 --> 00:08:17.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with their dearly departed?</b></Default>

c0000140
00:08:21.420 --> 00:08:22.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thankfully for the two of us,</b></Default>

c0000141
00:08:22.750 --> 00:08:25.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the Einsam's illusions
aren't a threat to mages</b></Default>

c0000142
00:08:25.140 --> 00:08:26.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who know to look
beyond their tricks.</b></Default>

c0000143
00:08:27.640 --> 00:08:29.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're easily dispersed
by high-density mana.</b></Default>

c0000144
00:08:30.550 --> 00:08:32.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Basic offensive magic
should do.</b></Default>

c0000145
00:08:33.430 --> 00:08:35.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, all I have to do
is shoot through the phantoms.</b></Default>

c0000146
00:08:38.560 --> 00:08:39.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Could you?</b></Default>

c0000147
00:08:40.770 --> 00:08:41.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, of course.</b></Default>

c0000148
00:08:42.650 --> 00:08:44.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Especially now
that I know they're fake.</b></Default>

c0000149
00:08:45.570 --> 00:08:47.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I once had to shoot
an illusion of my master</b></Default>

c0000150
00:08:47.950 --> 00:08:49.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>begging for her life.</b></Default>

c0000151
00:08:50.740 --> 00:08:52.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Though, to be fair,
her begging not to die</b></Default>

c0000152
00:08:52.780 --> 00:08:54.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>was a regular occurrence.</b></Default>

c0000153
00:08:54.610 --> 00:08:57.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, I can't say that
I felt particularly guilty.</b></Default>

c0000154
00:08:57.960 --> 00:08:59.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Regardless,
it certainly isn't fun.</b></Default>

c0000155
00:09:01.170 --> 00:09:02.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Why? Were you accustomed</b></Default>

c0000156
00:09:03.040 --> 00:09:04.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to hearing her
beg for her life?</b></Default>

c0000157
00:09:10.680 --> 00:09:12.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The mist is growing thicker.</b></Default>

c0000158
00:09:13.630 --> 00:09:14.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're not far.</b></Default>

c0000159
00:09:15.230 --> 00:09:16.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000160
00:09:16.600 --> 00:09:18.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you see a specter,
don't hesitate to shoot.</b></Default>

c0000161
00:09:24.520 --> 00:09:25.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HEITER]
Fern.</b></Default>

c0000162
00:09:25.700 --> 00:09:26.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Fern gasps]</b></Default>

c0000163
00:09:27.740 --> 00:09:28.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000164
00:09:30.900 --> 00:09:31.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
There it is.</b></Default>

c0000165
00:09:32.200 --> 00:09:33.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A phantom of the dead.</b></Default>

c0000166
00:09:36.160 --> 00:09:37.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No problem.</b></Default>

c0000167
00:09:38.330 --> 00:09:39.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just shoot.</b></Default>

c0000168
00:09:40.370 --> 00:09:41.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[smiling]</b></Default>

c0000169
00:09:41.830 --> 00:09:43.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Look at that mage.</b></Default>

c0000170
00:09:43.160 --> 00:09:45.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've surpassed
my wildest dreams, my dear.</b></Default>

c0000171
00:09:46.010 --> 00:09:47.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000172
00:09:47.630 --> 00:09:49.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I decided to come back
and say hello.</b></Default>

c0000173
00:09:50.130 --> 00:09:53.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A girl as good as you are
deserves a friendly haunting.</b></Default>

c0000174
00:09:53.590 --> 00:09:55.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]
Huh?</b></Default>

c0000175
00:09:57.140 --> 00:09:59.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[FERN] It knows.
-The path of the mage called,</b></Default>

c0000176
00:09:59.600 --> 00:10:01.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and you wisely followed.</b></Default>

c0000177
00:10:01.770 --> 00:10:02.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Since you were a child,</b></Default>

c0000178
00:10:03.020 --> 00:10:04.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>your love for magic
has been clear.</b></Default>

c0000179
00:10:04.140 --> 00:10:05.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
My cherished memories.</b></Default>

c0000180
00:10:05.780 --> 00:10:08.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-The first time I saw...
-[FERN] It knows all of them,</b></Default>

c0000181
00:10:08.820 --> 00:10:10.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and it's using them against me.</b></Default>

c0000182
00:10:11.650 --> 00:10:12.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How cruel.</b></Default>

c0000183
00:10:15.290 --> 00:10:16.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Need help?</b></Default>

c0000184
00:10:20.290 --> 00:10:21.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Seems you might.</b></Default>

c0000185
00:10:23.160 --> 00:10:24.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah?</b></Default>

c0000186
00:10:29.130 --> 00:10:30.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't expect to see Himmel.</b></Default>

c0000187
00:10:31.590 --> 00:10:33.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was sure it would show me
my master,</b></Default>

c0000188
00:10:33.380 --> 00:10:35.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>like the last one
I defeated did.</b></Default>

c0000189
00:10:37.020 --> 00:10:40.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Perhaps this means I've changed
since I last encountered one.</b></Default>

c0000190
00:10:43.970 --> 00:10:46.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Frieren, shoot.</b></Default>

c0000191
00:10:47.860 --> 00:10:48.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Impressive.</b></Default>

c0000192
00:10:49.730 --> 00:10:51.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's just what he'd say.</b></Default>

c0000193
00:10:51.780 --> 00:10:52.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

c0000194
00:10:53.940 --> 00:10:54.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000195
00:11:00.990 --> 00:11:01.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000196
00:11:03.370 --> 00:11:04.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000197
00:11:13.550 --> 00:11:15.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And now the mountain pass
is safe once more.</b></Default>

c0000198
00:11:17.260 --> 00:11:18.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That thing I just saw.</b></Default>

c0000199
00:11:19.430 --> 00:11:21.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was only
a phantom of Master Heiter.</b></Default>

c0000200
00:11:22.720 --> 00:11:23.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A shadow.</b></Default>

c0000201
00:11:24.390 --> 00:11:25.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Correct.</b></Default>

c0000202
00:11:29.070 --> 00:11:31.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's high time
we go see the real thing.</b></Default>

c0000203
00:11:32.400 --> 00:11:34.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If there's anywhere
we might find him,</b></Default>

c0000204
00:11:34.190 --> 00:11:35.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it would be Aureole.</b></Default>

c0000205
00:11:35.990 --> 00:11:36.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[smiles]</b></Default>

c0000206
00:11:37.990 --> 00:11:38.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
You're right.</b></Default>

c0000207
00:11:45.630 --> 00:11:47.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000208
00:11:49.920 --> 00:11:50.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's a dragon?</b></Default>

c0000209
00:11:52.420 --> 00:11:54.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've never seen one
in real life.</b></Default>

c0000210
00:11:55.800 --> 00:11:57.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Look at its nest.</b></Default>

c0000211
00:11:58.850 --> 00:12:00.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you see that grimoire?</b></Default>

c0000212
00:12:01.140 --> 00:12:03.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've been after that one
for a long time.</b></Default>

c0000213
00:12:03.930 --> 00:12:05.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
That doesn't surprise me.</b></Default>

c0000214
00:12:06.310 --> 00:12:08.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why's it there, of all places?</b></Default>

c0000215
00:12:08.810 --> 00:12:10.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Dragons are known
to seek out objects</b></Default>

c0000216
00:12:10.690 --> 00:12:12.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>infused with magic
to build their nests.</b></Default>

c0000217
00:12:14.230 --> 00:12:15.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's a solar dragon.</b></Default>

c0000218
00:12:16.240 --> 00:12:18.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No doubt it has dined
on many an adventurer.</b></Default>

c0000219
00:12:19.570 --> 00:12:22.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Grimoire or otherwise,
we should eliminate the beast.</b></Default>

c0000220
00:12:24.160 --> 00:12:25.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Be careful not to destroy
the nest.</b></Default>

c0000221
00:12:26.330 --> 00:12:27.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right.</b></Default>

c0000222
00:12:40.930 --> 00:12:43.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, uh,
that didn't do anything.</b></Default>

c0000223
00:12:44.090 --> 00:12:46.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They are
very resilient creatures.</b></Default>

c0000224
00:12:46.600 --> 00:12:48.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No choice, then. Run.</b></Default>

c0000225
00:12:50.940 --> 00:12:51.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[growling]</b></Default>

c0000226
00:12:54.480 --> 00:12:55.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000227
00:12:56.410 --> 00:12:57.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

c0000228
00:12:58.950 --> 00:13:01.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

c0000229
00:13:04.530 --> 00:13:07.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

c0000230
00:13:07.580 --> 00:13:08.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Finally lost it.</b></Default>

c0000231
00:13:09.580 --> 00:13:11.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This one's a fast flyer.</b></Default>

c0000232
00:13:12.000 --> 00:13:13.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No aerial battle for us.</b></Default>

c0000233
00:13:14.370 --> 00:13:15.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought...</b></Default>

c0000234
00:13:15.880 --> 00:13:17.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought I was gonna die
right there.</b></Default>

c0000235
00:13:18.590 --> 00:13:19.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's head back that way.</b></Default>

c0000236
00:13:20.590 --> 00:13:21.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If we continue to wear it down,</b></Default>

c0000237
00:13:22.010 --> 00:13:23.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the brute will eventually
give in.</b></Default>

c0000238
00:13:24.630 --> 00:13:25.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mm.</b></Default>

c0000239
00:13:28.440 --> 00:13:29.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good point.</b></Default>

c0000240
00:13:30.230 --> 00:13:31.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Playing tag with dragons</b></Default>

c0000241
00:13:31.560 --> 00:13:34.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is not within
a mage's job description.</b></Default>

c0000242
00:13:35.310 --> 00:13:36.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000243
00:13:38.740 --> 00:13:40.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll have to take on
another companion.</b></Default>

c0000244
00:13:44.400 --> 00:13:45.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A front-liner?</b></Default>

c0000245
00:13:45.710 --> 00:13:48.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN] Yes. You're
searching for one, aren't you?</b></Default>

c0000246
00:13:49.830 --> 00:13:51.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In a village
near Riegel Canyon,</b></Default>

c0000247
00:13:52.080 --> 00:13:53.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you'll find a warrior
named Stark.</b></Default>

c0000248
00:13:54.410 --> 00:13:56.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Pick him up on your way
into the northern lands.</b></Default>

c0000249
00:13:58.050 --> 00:13:59.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's my apprentice.</b></Default>

c0000250
00:14:00.300 --> 00:14:01.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right.</b></Default>

c0000251
00:14:02.090 --> 00:14:03.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is he any good?</b></Default>

c0000252
00:14:04.050 --> 00:14:05.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000253
00:14:10.770 --> 00:14:11.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE MERCHANT 5A]
I'll make you a deal!</b></Default>

c0000254
00:14:13.020 --> 00:14:14.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE CUSTOMER 5A]
How much for the whole block?</b></Default>

c0000255
00:14:15.180 --> 00:14:17.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hard to think
there's a dragon near.</b></Default>

c0000256
00:14:17.190 --> 00:14:18.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's so peaceful.</b></Default>

c0000257
00:14:19.110 --> 00:14:20.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>'Tis indeed.</b></Default>

c0000258
00:14:22.570 --> 00:14:23.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FREN]
I've been meaning to ask,</b></Default>

c0000259
00:14:24.400 --> 00:14:27.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what sort of spell does
that grimoire contain, anyway?</b></Default>

c0000260
00:14:28.450 --> 00:14:30.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One that lets you
see through clothes.</b></Default>

c0000261
00:14:31.370 --> 00:14:32.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000262
00:14:33.660 --> 00:14:34.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You really do gather</b></Default>

c0000263
00:14:34.950 --> 00:14:37.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>only the strangest of spells,
Mistress Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000264
00:14:38.010 --> 00:14:39.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That is my hobby.</b></Default>

c0000265
00:14:40.550 --> 00:14:42.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But this one is practical, too.</b></Default>

c0000266
00:14:43.010 --> 00:14:45.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Depending on what
the user views as clothing,</b></Default>

c0000267
00:14:45.720 --> 00:14:46.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it could reveal
hidden weaponry, or--</b></Default>

c0000268
00:14:46.890 --> 00:14:47.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[WOMAN 4A]
Travelers,</b></Default>

c0000269
00:14:47.970 --> 00:14:49.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>may I have a moment
of your time?</b></Default>

c0000270
00:14:50.220 --> 00:14:51.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[BOTH]
Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000271
00:14:51.470 --> 00:14:53.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mister Stark would like
to meet the two of you.</b></Default>

c0000272
00:14:55.140 --> 00:14:56.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That saves us
a fair bit of trouble.</b></Default>

c0000273
00:15:01.440 --> 00:15:03.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was three years back now.</b></Default>

c0000274
00:15:04.030 --> 00:15:05.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The dragon attacked,</b></Default>

c0000275
00:15:05.620 --> 00:15:07.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>nearly destroying the village.</b></Default>

c0000276
00:15:08.490 --> 00:15:10.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[whimpering]</b></Default>

c0000277
00:15:11.490 --> 00:15:12.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.
[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000278
00:15:14.990 --> 00:15:16.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[WOMAN 4A]
That's when he appeared,</b></Default>

c0000279
00:15:16.960 --> 00:15:18.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the brave Mister Stark.</b></Default>

c0000280
00:15:19.750 --> 00:15:21.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The dragon was fierce,</b></Default>

c0000281
00:15:21.090 --> 00:15:22.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but our brave hero
didn't break.</b></Default>

c0000282
00:15:23.050 --> 00:15:25.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After a long standoff,
the monster flew away!</b></Default>

c0000283
00:15:26.180 --> 00:15:29.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was a sight to behold.
Since that day...</b></Default>

c0000284
00:15:29.390 --> 00:15:31.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-he has lived alongside us
in the village,</b></Default>

c0000285
00:15:31.350 --> 00:15:33.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and that dragon
has been too scared</b></Default>

c0000286
00:15:33.260 --> 00:15:35.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to rear its ugly head
ever again.</b></Default>

c0000287
00:15:35.650 --> 00:15:37.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Three whole years of peace.</b></Default>

c0000288
00:15:37.650 --> 00:15:38.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000289
00:15:39.480 --> 00:15:42.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Perfect. He sounds like
just the person we need.</b></Default>

c0000290
00:15:42.730 --> 00:15:44.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The dragon's done for.</b></Default>

c0000291
00:15:44.900 --> 00:15:46.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I hope you're right.</b></Default>

c0000292
00:15:48.660 --> 00:15:51.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[BOY 4A] Do you think I can be
a strong warrior like you?</b></Default>

c0000293
00:15:52.240 --> 00:15:53.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
Sure, you can.</b></Default>

c0000294
00:15:53.910 --> 00:15:55.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But being a warrior's rougher
than it looks.</b></Default>

c0000295
00:15:56.790 --> 00:15:57.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[smiles]</b></Default>

c0000296
00:15:58.130 --> 00:16:00.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?
It's Grandma!</b></Default>

c0000297
00:16:02.920 --> 00:16:04.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both smiling]</b></Default>

c0000298
00:16:04.840 --> 00:16:05.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[smiles]</b></Default>

c0000299
00:16:08.720 --> 00:16:11.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, you're the ones who've been
messing with the dragon.</b></Default>

c0000300
00:16:12.180 --> 00:16:13.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't get that thing
too worked up.</b></Default>

c0000301
00:16:14.260 --> 00:16:15.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You'll put the whole village
in danger.</b></Default>

c0000302
00:16:16.610 --> 00:16:17.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Dragons are serious.</b></Default>

c0000303
00:16:18.150 --> 00:16:20.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're not the fairy tale
creatures you think they are.</b></Default>

c0000304
00:16:22.520 --> 00:16:24.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One of them gave me this scar.</b></Default>

c0000305
00:16:24.400 --> 00:16:25.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was fighting a shadow dragon,
and it--</b></Default>

c0000306
00:16:25.780 --> 00:16:27.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's child's play
as far as injuries go.</b></Default>

c0000307
00:16:30.120 --> 00:16:32.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My master put you up to this,
didn't he?</b></Default>

c0000308
00:16:32.910 --> 00:16:33.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who are you?</b></Default>

c0000309
00:16:34.820 --> 00:16:36.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am known as Freiren the Mage.</b></Default>

c0000310
00:16:37.210 --> 00:16:38.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000311
00:16:39.790 --> 00:16:41.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] Hey, Gran,
mind giving us some privacy?</b></Default>

c0000312
00:16:43.540 --> 00:16:44.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's all right.</b></Default>

c0000313
00:16:44.790 --> 00:16:46.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're acquaintances
of my master.</b></Default>

c0000314
00:16:46.470 --> 00:16:49.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000315
00:16:52.390 --> 00:16:53.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
Don't hold back.</b></Default>

c0000316
00:16:53.890 --> 00:16:54.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He must be furious.</b></Default>

c0000317
00:16:55.470 --> 00:16:57.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I left without so much
as a word.</b></Default>

c0000318
00:16:58.270 --> 00:16:59.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Stark.</b></Default>

c0000319
00:16:59.520 --> 00:17:01.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You have no reason
to remain in this village.</b></Default>

c0000320
00:17:02.400 --> 00:17:04.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why haven't you defeated
the dragon?</b></Default>

c0000321
00:17:05.230 --> 00:17:06.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tell me what you want
and maybe</b></Default>

c0000322
00:17:06.610 --> 00:17:07.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll think about sharing.</b></Default>

c0000323
00:17:08.820 --> 00:17:10.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you're here to send me
back to my master,</b></Default>

c0000324
00:17:10.610 --> 00:17:11.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you can forget about it.</b></Default>

c0000325
00:17:12.950 --> 00:17:14.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're in need of a warrior</b></Default>

c0000326
00:17:14.320 --> 00:17:15.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and would like for you
to join us.</b></Default>

c0000327
00:17:16.370 --> 00:17:18.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Though before that,
we would appreciate your help</b></Default>

c0000328
00:17:18.500 --> 00:17:19.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in defeating the dragon.</b></Default>

c0000329
00:17:20.710 --> 00:17:22.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want the grimoire
in its nest.</b></Default>

c0000330
00:17:23.460 --> 00:17:24.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why's that?</b></Default>

c0000331
00:17:24.750 --> 00:17:27.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a hobby.
No particular reason.</b></Default>

c0000332
00:17:28.180 --> 00:17:30.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're dealing
with a solar dragon.</b></Default>

c0000333
00:17:30.680 --> 00:17:32.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You don't fight it
without a good reason.</b></Default>

c0000334
00:17:34.510 --> 00:17:35.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000335
00:17:39.310 --> 00:17:40.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[BOTH] Aah!
-Ah!</b></Default>

c0000336
00:17:40.480 --> 00:17:42.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs]
That's amazing!</b></Default>

c0000337
00:17:42.560 --> 00:17:43.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Aah!
-Woo!</b></Default>

c0000338
00:17:43.890 --> 00:17:44.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
You're right.</b></Default>

c0000339
00:17:46.240 --> 00:17:48.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mine is that a fool
once praised me</b></Default>

c0000340
00:17:48.240 --> 00:17:49.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for the spells I collected.</b></Default>

c0000341
00:17:50.610 --> 00:17:52.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that enough of a reason?</b></Default>

c0000342
00:17:53.530 --> 00:17:54.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
For a little praise?</b></Default>

c0000343
00:17:55.400 --> 00:17:56.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Aah.</b></Default>

c0000344
00:17:57.000 --> 00:17:58.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000345
00:17:58.910 --> 00:18:00.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's ridiculous.</b></Default>

c0000346
00:18:00.160 --> 00:18:01.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Agreed.</b></Default>

c0000347
00:18:02.710 --> 00:18:04.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] I don't mind
joining your party.</b></Default>

c0000348
00:18:04.460 --> 00:18:05.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000349
00:18:05.460 --> 00:18:07.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can tell my master
put you up to this.</b></Default>

c0000350
00:18:08.510 --> 00:18:09.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But no matter.</b></Default>

c0000351
00:18:09.920 --> 00:18:12.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My priority is taking out
the solar dragon.</b></Default>

c0000352
00:18:12.970 --> 00:18:15.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've had difficulties
defeating it on my own.</b></Default>

c0000353
00:18:16.770 --> 00:18:19.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For you,
it'd be no issue, right?</b></Default>

c0000354
00:18:20.230 --> 00:18:22.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, not at all,
if you can keep the beast</b></Default>

c0000355
00:18:22.180 --> 00:18:23.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>busy for 30 seconds.</b></Default>

c0000356
00:18:24.680 --> 00:18:25.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Loud and clear.</b></Default>

c0000357
00:18:26.900 --> 00:18:28.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just 30 seconds, huh?</b></Default>

c0000358
00:18:30.490 --> 00:18:32.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And that really has to be
my job?</b></Default>

c0000359
00:18:33.030 --> 00:18:35.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is there some kind of joke
that I'm missing here?</b></Default>

c0000360
00:18:36.000 --> 00:18:38.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't say
that I'm very surprised.</b></Default>

c0000361
00:18:38.830 --> 00:18:39.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tell me, Stark.</b></Default>

c0000362
00:18:40.080 --> 00:18:41.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just how many monsters
have you fought?</b></Default>

c0000363
00:18:42.200 --> 00:18:43.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A big, fat zero, okay?!</b></Default>

c0000364
00:18:44.120 --> 00:18:46.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't abandon me, Frieren.
I need your help!</b></Default>

c0000365
00:18:47.340 --> 00:18:49.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] I worked up the guts
to confront the dragon.</b></Default>

c0000366
00:18:50.260 --> 00:18:52.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I was so terrified,
I couldn't move a muscle!</b></Default>

c0000367
00:18:53.630 --> 00:18:55.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, come on.</b></Default>

c0000368
00:18:55.420 --> 00:18:57.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That thing slices through
houses like they're veggies!</b></Default>

c0000369
00:18:58.810 --> 00:19:01.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A human being doesn't stand
a chance against it!</b></Default>

c0000370
00:19:02.270 --> 00:19:04.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I figured that it spared me
on a whim, but...</b></Default>

c0000371
00:19:05.430 --> 00:19:07.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[cheering]</b></Default>

c0000372
00:19:08.860 --> 00:19:11.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The dragon stopped attacking
the village after that,</b></Default>

c0000373
00:19:11.150 --> 00:19:12.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I was treated like a hero.</b></Default>

c0000374
00:19:13.480 --> 00:19:15.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The villagers are too nice
for their own good!</b></Default>

c0000375
00:19:16.450 --> 00:19:18.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A strong young man like you
should eat up!</b></Default>

c0000376
00:19:18.620 --> 00:19:19.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Stark! After supper,</b></Default>

c0000377
00:19:20.040 --> 00:19:22.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you gotta show me
all your latest moves!</b></Default>

c0000378
00:19:22.290 --> 00:19:23.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's no way
that I could leave this place</b></Default>

c0000379
00:19:23.950 --> 00:19:25.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>even if I wanted to.</b></Default>

c0000380
00:19:25.960 --> 00:19:27.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This one's no good.</b></Default>

c0000381
00:19:27.590 --> 00:19:30.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We should get going
and find someone serious.</b></Default>

c0000382
00:19:30.300 --> 00:19:32.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please don't leave me here
to rot!</b></Default>

c0000383
00:19:33.340 --> 00:19:35.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No. He can hold off the dragon.</b></Default>

c0000384
00:19:36.720 --> 00:19:37.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm certain of it.</b></Default>

c0000385
00:19:38.430 --> 00:19:41.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fine, but it'll take more than
a pat on the back.</b></Default>

c0000386
00:19:42.560 --> 00:19:43.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000387
00:19:52.320 --> 00:19:53.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000388
00:20:02.280 --> 00:20:03.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, Stark.</b></Default>

c0000389
00:20:03.620 --> 00:20:05.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You have till tomorrow morning.</b></Default>

c0000390
00:20:06.710 --> 00:20:07.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Think it all through.</b></Default>

c0000391
00:20:08.540 --> 00:20:11.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know as well as I do
you can't keep the hero act up.</b></Default>

c0000392
00:20:16.970 --> 00:20:19.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000393
00:20:21.680 --> 00:20:22.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

c0000394
00:20:25.900 --> 00:20:27.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE VILLAGER 5A]
I heard you met Mister Stark!</b></Default>

c0000395
00:20:28.690 --> 00:20:30.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A fine young man, isn't he?</b></Default>

c0000396
00:20:30.560 --> 00:20:31.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's just lovely.</b></Default>

c0000397
00:20:31.810 --> 00:20:33.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When we cook for him,
it seems</b></Default>

c0000398
00:20:33.110 --> 00:20:35.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>his stomach is almost
as big as his smile!</b></Default>

c0000399
00:20:36.200 --> 00:20:38.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Everyone really seems
to love that guy.</b></Default>

c0000400
00:20:39.070 --> 00:20:40.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sure that they do.</b></Default>

c0000401
00:20:40.160 --> 00:20:42.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He struck me
as a kind sort of person.</b></Default>

c0000402
00:20:42.990 --> 00:20:44.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Maybe so.</b></Default>

c0000403
00:20:45.240 --> 00:20:47.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was distracted
by his immense cowardice.</b></Default>

c0000404
00:20:48.420 --> 00:20:50.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] The lad is
a little yellow-bellied,</b></Default>

c0000405
00:20:50.960 --> 00:20:52.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but let's think back
to your first time</b></Default>

c0000406
00:20:52.710 --> 00:20:54.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>going up against a monster.</b></Default>

c0000407
00:20:54.420 --> 00:20:55.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grins]</b></Default>

c0000408
00:20:56.090 --> 00:20:57.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Never mind.
Let's think forward.</b></Default>

c0000409
00:21:01.010 --> 00:21:02.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
You were cute once.</b></Default>

c0000410
00:21:02.720 --> 00:21:04.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not only are you
taller than me now,</b></Default>

c0000411
00:21:04.390 --> 00:21:05.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but scarier, too.</b></Default>

c0000412
00:21:07.310 --> 00:21:08.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What I want to know</b></Default>

c0000413
00:21:08.810 --> 00:21:10.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is why the dragon
hasn't been attacking.</b></Default>

c0000414
00:21:11.520 --> 00:21:12.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who can say?</b></Default>

c0000415
00:21:12.980 --> 00:21:14.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It might be
bored of this place.</b></Default>

c0000416
00:21:14.810 --> 00:21:15.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or perhaps...</b></Default>

c0000417
00:21:15.950 --> 00:21:17.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

c0000418
00:21:18.530 --> 00:21:19.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What was that sound?</b></Default>

c0000419
00:21:20.490 --> 00:21:21.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Stark, I imagine.</b></Default>

c0000420
00:21:22.490 --> 00:21:23.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000421
00:21:23.860 --> 00:21:25.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] If you're curious,
you should go check on him.</b></Default>

c0000422
00:21:26.540 --> 00:21:27.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm going to bed.</b></Default>

c0000423
00:21:28.170 --> 00:21:29.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

c0000424
00:21:45.130 --> 00:21:47.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Right. Is he any good?</b></Default>

c0000425
00:21:50.810 --> 00:21:53.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN] When his village
was attacked by monsters,</b></Default>

c0000426
00:21:53.440 --> 00:21:55.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>he fled and never looked back.</b></Default>

c0000427
00:21:56.240 --> 00:21:58.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's a coward
who left his home to burn.</b></Default>

c0000428
00:22:00.900 --> 00:22:01.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's like me.</b></Default>

c0000429
00:22:04.860 --> 00:22:06.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why
I hammered everything</b></Default>

c0000430
00:22:06.580 --> 00:22:08.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know into the boy.</b></Default>

c0000431
00:22:08.960 --> 00:22:11.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now, he's finally ready
to fight for someone</b></Default>

c0000432
00:22:11.250 --> 00:22:12.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>other than himself.</b></Default>

c0000433
00:22:14.040 --> 00:22:15.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've sold me.</b></Default>

c0000434
00:22:15.920 --> 00:22:16.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He is any good.</b></Default>

c0000435
00:22:22.300 --> 00:22:23.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000436
00:22:25.550 --> 00:22:26.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Aah!</b></Default>

c0000437
00:22:38.240 --> 00:22:41.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] I see now. Your training
is what made this fissure.</b></Default>

c0000438
00:24:20.250 --> 00:24:21.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAN 5A]
The passage of time is cruel.</b></Default>

c0000439
00:24:22.090 --> 00:24:23.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE GUARD 5A] Do not
cause any trouble in this town.</b></Default>

c0000440
00:24:23.790 --> 00:24:24.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
He must've been disappointed.</b></Default>

c0000441
00:24:25.880 --> 00:24:27.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Even the way
they tremble is the same.</b></Default>

c0000442
00:24:27.600 --> 00:24:30.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] I'm Stark,
the hero of this village.</b></Default>

